data.description: Great family home with SALTWATER IN-GROUND POOL, in a desirable Canyon De Flores!!! 4 bedroom, 2 baths, 2.5 car garage is in turn-key condition.  Great room has gas log fireplace.  Nice kitchen with gas oven/ range and fridge stays.  Main bedroom has double sinks, Garden tub, Step-in shower, and a large walk-in closet!  Upgraded ceiling fixtures with ceiling fans.  Freshly painted inside and outside (09/2023).  Roof was inspected and maintained (09/2023).  The Saltwater Pool has been upkept by Thunder Mountain Pool.  Nice block fenced backyard with Mountain Views.  Enjoy your family activities at the large block fenced backyard with covered patio, pool, and nice mountain views!!!  Seller may give the 2 bedroom carpets allowance, pending negotiation.  Easy to show, use Keysafe
